                  </persName>
            ; I do not remember the numbers; I paid them to Mr. Medcalf; there were a 500 l. a 200 l. a 100 l. and a 10 l. there was only one 10 l. bank note; I paid the same identical notes to Mr. Medcalf.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17861213-113-person1054">
