             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am one of the clerks of Messrs. Clark and Co's house: On the 18th of October, I recollect some notes being handed to me from Mr. Medcalf; this is my book, entered by myself at the time; the sum was 810 l. they were received from 
               <persName id="t17861213-113-person1056">
                  James
                   Annesdale
               <interp inst="t17861213-113-person1056" type="surname" value="Annesdale"></interp>
