                     <interp inst="t17861213-113-person1059" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , at Liverpool? - I did not.</p>
               <p>Did you ever receive that letter with the bank notes? - No.</p>
               <p>Court to J. Tennant. Did you put the letter in the Post-office yourself? - No, I gave it to 
               <persName id="t17861213-113-person1060">
                  Jonathan
                   Hitchen
               <interp inst="t17861213-113-person1060" type="surname" value="Hitchen"></interp>
