                     <interp inst="t17861213-113-person1073" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am the principal sorter in the <placeName id="t17861213-113-crimeloc571">general Penny-post-office, in Throgmorton-street</placeName>
